Package com.milk.uberchat.gui

Interface Summary
ContainsTree This interface is for those components that contain a tree to interact with.
 

Class Summary
ChannelsPanel This is a panel which keeps track of all the active channels for a particular identity, with sub-trees for the users in each channel.
CreateSystemPanel This is a panel which has fill-in fields for the parameters of a connection, along with a "create" button.
EntityTreeCellRenderer This is the TreeCellRenderer to use for rendering ChatEntities in trees.
FunctionsPanel This class is a panel which allows one to perform some common chat functions (sending messages, changing nicknames, setting topics).
IdentitiesPanel This is a panel which keeps track of all the active identities.
LocusPanel This is a panel which has all the guts for doing interaction in a particular locus.
Main This is the main body of the UI uberchat front end.
MasterControl This is the master control object for UberChat.
UsersPanel This is a panel which keeps track of all the active users for a particular identity, with sub-trees for the channels each is on
